page.title: 08A day in the life of Julie.
page.content: I wake up at 7.15,go downstairs for my breakfast of Weetabix,toast and a drink.At 7.35 I wash and dress.Then I feed our animals. At 8.30 I walk to school,which takes 15 minutes.My school is St.John's Primary School.School starts at 9.00.First break is at 10.35 and lasts for 15 minutes.We usually do Maths next.Lunch is at 12.15.In the Summertime we sit outside.Play lasts until 1.15.During the afternoon,we sometimes have country dancing or athletics.Last break is at 2.30 and school finishes at 3.30. When I get home I take the dog for a walk.At 6.00 I have my tea.Afterwards I feed the animals.I go to bed at 9.30 or 10.00. Julie Burns
